comments: Capela (HOU) is already in Lillard's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Lillard (POR) places his hand momentarily on Capela's (HOU) side before correcting.
Hunter (ATL) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he maintains his pivot foot on the perimeter.
Kanter (POR) legally contests Young's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Anthony (POR) and Capela (ATL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Hunter (ATL) moves laterally into Lillard's (POR) path and affects his SQBR.
Huerter (ATL) is moving alongside Lillard's (POR) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Young (ATL) applies a stayed hand to Trent Jr.'s (POR) body during his upward shooting motion, and contact is marginal.
Jones Jr. (POR) and Capela (ATL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Capela (ATL) is already in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Kanter (POR) extends his arm forward into Young's (ATL) path but he collapses his arm as marginal contact with Young occurs.
Kanter (POR) legally contests Young's (ATL) shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) is moving alongside Lillard's (POR) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Anthony (POR) is bracing for the contact from Young (ATL) and releases away from the contact.
Young (ATL) briefly has a hand placed on Anthony (POR) during his shooting motion but the contact is marginal and he immediately removes his hand.
Anthony (POR) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Huerter (ATL) and Jones Jr. (POR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.

After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined Lillard (POR) established a legal guarding position outside the RA prior to contact with Young (ATL), and the call on the floor (offensive foul) was confirmed.
Hunter (ATL) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Kanter (POR) keeps his foot planted to the floor and does not intentionally kick the ball on the play.
Hunter (ATL) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Lillard (POR) cleanly deflects the ball away from Young (ATL).
